{"tid":1828223,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有食唔食罪大惡極","createTime":"2020-01-17T15:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T17:14:11.000Z","uid":178742,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e948b1808022e61ac3e380b243f4122ff6810167","tid":1828223,"uid":178742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"想當年阿叔我20歲A0仲係青頭時<br />\n<br />\n有晚唱完K去左男同事屋企吹水&amp;過夜 我瞓地下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瞓到半夜竟然有條靚女返黎（唱K都係到，後尾知佢係清巴做拳手） 佢醉醉地先係瞓係我隔離話凍 跟著攬著我 最後仲琴上黎我到<br />\n<br />\n好可惜當年我連女仔手都未拖過嚇到呆左 無食住上<br />\n<br />\n結果條女琴著我係到DIY左陣就去左沖涼返黎吹水吹通宵<br />\n<br />\n每次諗返都覺得堅香艷&amp;後悔點解當時咁柒做左正人君子坐懷不亂<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打有無試過到嘴邊的肉都無膽起筷？"},{"pid":"711905232a1b77fa0190600f3781e2ba0325a3e8","tid":1828223,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人真事？"},{"pid":"903bf022dba8d6dfafa2aba0dd0dbdb913b06d4f","tid":1828223,"uid":178742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"711905232a1b77fa0190600f3781e2ba0325a3e8","tid":1828223,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人真事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"堅真人真事 親身經歷"},{"pid":"6b94505c361824920a599ad92a8d6cb87208750b","tid":1828223,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T15:33:13.000Z","msg":"感同身受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾經有兩個大波學生妹係口邊<br />\n一個把聲粗一個隻腳粗就棄左<br />\n諗住大把機會何必食粗野<br />\n當時又唔識<br />\n真大波&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;everything<br />\n唉&hellip;不想再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr